### Get all organization users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/organizationusers

### Get specific organization user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/organizationusers/organization/{{organizationId}}/user/{{userId}}

### Get all users in an organization
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/organizationusers/organization/{{organizationId}}

### Get all organizations for a user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/organizationusers/user/{{userId}}

### Get active users in an organization
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/organizationusers/organization/{{organizationId}}/active

### Get active organizations for a user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/organizationusers/user/{{userId}}/active

### Get organization users by role
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/organizationusers/role/Admin

### Get organization users by organization and role
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/organizationusers/organization/{{organizationId}}/role/Admin

### Get organization users with details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/organizationusers/organization/{{organizationId}}/with-details

### Create organization user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/organizationusers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizationId": "{{organizationId}}",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "role": "Member",
  "isActive": true
}

### Update organization user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/organizationusers/organization/{{organizationId}}/user/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "Admin",
  "isActive": true
}

### Deactivate organization user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/organizationusers/organization/{{organizationId}}/user/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}

### Check if user is active in organization
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/organizationusers/organization/{{organizationId}}/user/{{userId}}/is-active

### Delete organization user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/organizationusers/organization/{{organizationId}}/user/{{userId}} 